quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"(Ŵajonasile achinsyene ndembo) kuti ajendelechele Makuraishi."
  106,2,"Panyendele jao jamaulendo ga chuku (kuja ku Yemeni) ni chawu (kuja ku Shami kumalonda mwantunjelele)."
  106,3,"Basi an'galagatileje M'mbuje jwa aji Nyumba (ja Likaaba)."
  106,4,"Ajula jwaŵapele yakulya ligongo lyasala, ni kwaŵambasya ku woga."
